sql_query: SELECT EXTRACT(YEAR FROM incident_datetime) AS year, COUNT(*) AS incident_count, AVG(CASE WHEN severity = 'High' THEN 1 WHEN severity = 'Medium' THEN 0.5 WHEN severity = 'Low' THEN 0 ELSE 0 END) AS avg_severity FROM og_incidents GROUP BY EXTRACT(YEAR FROM incident_datetime) ORDER BY year;
